Inputs

Form control inputs.

textInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

searchInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

emailInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

urlInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

telephoneInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

passwordInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

numberInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

colorInput(value = NULL, placeholder = NULL, ..., id = NULL)

Arguments

placeholder

A character string specifying placeholder text for the input, defaults to NULL.
...

Named arguments passed as HTML attributes to the input. Specify value to give the input a default value. Specify placeholder to give the input hint text about the expected value of the input.
id

A character string specifying the id of the textual input, defaults to NULL. If specified, a reactive value is available to the shiny server function.
label

A character vector specifying a label for the input, defaults to NULL. If a label is specified it is advised, though not necessary, to also specify an id for the input.

Details

  • text - Single-line text input, linebreaks are removed.

  • search - Single-line text input for search strings, linebreaks are removed.

  • email - Single-line text input for email addresses, validated to contain the empty string or a valid email address.

  • url - Single-line text input for URLs, validated to contain the empty string or valid absolute URL.

  • tel - Single-line text input for telephone numbers, syntax is not enforced.

  • password - Single-line text input for password, value is obscured.

  • number - Number picker.

  • datetime - Date and time picker, no time zone.

  • date - Year, month, and day picker, no time.

  • month - Month and year picker, no time zone.

  • week - Week of year picker.

  • time - Time picker.

  • color - Color picker.

See also

Other inputs: button, groupInput, radioInput, selectInput
